To install:

1) Check you have the following installed:
   - Parallel::ForkManager (libparallel-forkmanager-perl
     package under GNU/Debian)
   - Net::SSH::Perl (available from CPAN)
   - Getopt::Std (part of the standard Perl distribution)
   - File::Basename (part of the standard Perl distribution)
2) Make sure SSHatter.pl is executable (chmod u+x
   SSHatter.pl)

The latest version of SSHatter can always be found at
<http://www.nth-dimension.org.uk/>.
